title: World of Warcraft Comics
description:
It is just a recompilation of several other torrents, including the 4th issue of the ashbringer mini-serie (which I didnt find on torrents).

This compilation includes:
World of Warcraft ongoing #00 to #19
World of Warcraft Ashbringer mini-series #01 to #04
Warcraft_The_Sunwell_Trilogy #01 to #03

And don't forgot, if you really like them, go buy them in your local comic shop!
